Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔瑪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:33.08,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人看到煙火時 喊的口頭語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞莉基菈那傢伙 沒把義眼的小鬼殺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是難得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然被自己拳頭的力量彈飛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 敵人的力量也同時被削弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出拳時要把馬步紮穩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是基本常識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有我「纏繞」你早就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不妙 那樣你也會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特羅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠再這樣一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你真還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 託大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又沒在誇你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.84,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,居然隨隨便便就下跪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能行動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 拜託這次要選擇可以紮穩馬步的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可愛呢 道格·哈瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有外表還可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷歐怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:56.93,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連你也來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏執王為什麼偏執 我稍微有點懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有必要待在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請放了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說有必要的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種狀況下你要我幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如戀愛話題的相談？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊 克勞斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有喜歡的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在意的女生至少有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 稍微在意的女生總有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那種的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 其實我對那種很不擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒法交流嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少給我吐出一個來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要裝傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不知是說喜歡好 還是說在意好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有個跟我處得很好的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個無趣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定還有別的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我去告白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對那個女孩子說我喜歡你試試看？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全搞不懂現在的情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 道格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 迪特羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你為什麼要衝向那個怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:13:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你啊 好像什麼都不知道的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前你不是已經把亞莉基菈的事情忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是嚇我一跳 突然衝出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛呢 就是推啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開槍開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後推到頂端的人贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那時你不是很興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是你所願 我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們是一心同體的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子也相當不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我完全不知道怎麼從這裡逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細想想啊 雷歐納魯德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在這裡的話會被不斷的遭受拷問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽得到嗎 雷歐納魯德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…這個番茄醬太硬喲 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.14,Default_top,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用咳嗽回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yes是一次 no是兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事不宜遲 你聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所在的那輛怪物卡車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在就要破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 硬剛正面並沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員將盡全力削弱其衝勢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你負責支配怪物卡車的視野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誘導其路線直線前往舊亞貝紐公園
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你辦得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辦得到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配視野 朝著前進方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:14:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我轉
