Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錨 裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 哈瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特羅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這附近的血集中到拳頭上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去 會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑 道格·哈瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是肉體被剝離了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普羅迪和哈瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般鐵拳 改
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標車輛被打飛散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數億鐵屑落在赫爾沙雷姆茲·羅特的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說死傷人數有數百 也有說有數十萬的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒有一個確鑿的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好傳達給亞莉基菈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了伙食費我還是可以努力一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得你也有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不要浪費了的好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個身體很方便的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縫了五針
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了快點回家睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兒真是亂七八糟的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看電影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 真的出現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 如果害你被罵就不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被罵什麼的都不在乎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是突然這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被S了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 相信我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是雙胞胎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在找哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱倆哪裡像兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不像好不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是你那樣的精英啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 不要用那種眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想一直看到我褲子裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 難得你帶人家來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我道歉才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶你看這樣的喜劇也能讓你哭成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是我真的有點想哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺和我家很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家也是妹妹比較出色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然是哥哥 卻經常給她添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不像樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷歐是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲喲喲 人類諸君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我墮落王菲姆特來下期預告了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒想到有同一個角色來做預告的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真是不長記性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到有一天我會畏懼人類的墮落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.97,0:24:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 血界戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.57,0:24:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't forget to Don't forget me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.91,0:24:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不要忘記自己是誰
